Vault indexing commands

Usage: obsidian-cli-inspector index [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  index  Index the vault (scan and parse all files)
  help   Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -o, --output <FORMAT>  Output in JSON format (for machine integration)
  -h, --help             Print help
